bio.openEndedText: Love traveling and finding good people in different places. Love playing sports and watching them as well. Love eating street food and outdoors activities. My dream car is a BMW M series.

Greetings, Turo community! I’m Kenton Fox, your car enthusiast host, ready to make your car rental experience seamless and enjoyable.

My passion for responsible hosting is reflected in my commitment to maintaining vehicles in top-notch condition and ensuring a hassle-free experience for every guest. Your safety and satisfaction are my top priorities.

Beyond the world of car rentals, my favorite vacation spots include the vibrant energy of Las Vegas, the coastal charm of San Diego, and the magical adventures of Orlando. These places hold a special spot in my heart, and I'm eager to share travel tips and recommendations with you.

When I'm not managing Turo bookings, you'll find me engaged in various hobbies. I have a competitive streak when it comes to dirt bike racing with my family, thrilling races with RC cars, and perfecting tricks on my skateboard. Additionally, I enjoy the tranquility of mountain bike riding and embarking on road trips with my loved ones.

As a car enthusiast, I have a dream – to cruise around in a yellow Porsche 911. Your bookings on Turo are helping me turn this dream into reality in time, and I'm grateful for your support in reaching this automotive milestone.

Feel confident choosing one of my vehicles for your next adventure. I look forward to sharing my love for cars and providing you with a memorable Turo experience. Safe travels!
